{
  "stem": "3453.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Camp, I thought they were building barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was barracks, but they're wooden barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not-- it was, you know, it's like a temporary thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said they are bringing in the prisoners of war and we-- we-- we-- we wanted to believe, because sometimes your mind does not want to-- to--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, I will, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When came our turn, I was almost to the end of the-- of the group, because my name was Szyr, all my family name.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my family and everybody were almost to the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This German was standing down there and-- with a big list of the people who are living in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was marking off anybody who was not present, marking it off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It did not make sense at that time to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, like it would be somebody would go on an outing, on a-- on a-- on a-- some-- just for a-- for a-- some kind of-- you know, he was marking it off.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we find out why did they did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they wanted to know how many people remained and how many they have to still look for to be killed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I remember right behind the gate, there was this-- we were surrounded with the-- with the Nazi was-- was going-- and-- and this guy who was standing down there and marking off the name, his face was red, I remember, and I think he stunk with alcohol.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He couldn't, I bet he couldn't stomach maybe this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they took us in behind the gate, we were surrounded by the Ukrainian and-- and this German, and I remember he was wearing a black armband with a white skeleton.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
